runs.comm: short and nipping in, Salman is fortunate to get an inside edge as he runs across for a single
pushes the ball down the leg side this time around as the ball defies the diving keeper on its way to fine leg boundary

first blood ! on the fuller length on the middle and leg, Akmal moves across and pushes it to mid on only to find Salman far down the pitch as Mahmudullah has enough time to come running across to the bowlers end and whip the bails off
on the middle stump, Kamran tucks it away to square leg
fuller on the off stump, Akmal reaches for the delivery but pushes it straight to point
short on the off stump, Akmal defends on the backfoot
double strike now as Kamran gropes for a ball pitching outside the off stump on a good length and coming in, and gets an inside edge sounding the death knell for himself as he finds himself bowled
fuller on the middle and leg stump, Younis punches it to mid on for a single
short outside the off stump, Misbah pushes it to point off the backfoot to point
on a good length on the middle stump, defends on the frontfoot
on a good length outside the off stump, pushes it to cover as they run across for a  quick single
fuller on the leg stump, Misbah pushes it to midwicket and sets off and whats more gets four more gift wrapped as overthrow results
fuller on the off stump, Younis pushes it to cover on the frontfoot
short and wide outside off, almost begging to be hit. Misbah rocks back and unleashes the cut shot behind point for a boundary
on a good length outside the off stump as Misbah lets it go to the keeper
on the off stump, Misbah flicks to midwicket to pick up a single
on a good length outside the off stump, has Younis reaching for it as he pushes it to point to pick up a single
on a good length on the middle stump, Misbah gives it all the respect it deserves as he defends on the frontfoot
outside the off stump, Misbah steers it to third man for a single
lures Misbah into the wild slog with a slower ball outside off as Misbah slogs but misses
fuller on the off stump, Misbah's arm does not fail him this time round as he lofts it to long on for a huge six. Beautiful hand eye coordination that
on the leg stump, Misbah pushes it to midwicket and sets off and would be miles out if Shakib's throw had found it's target
on the off stump, defends on the frontfoot
outside the off stump, Younis gets his frontfoot out of the way and drives but gets an outside edge to third man for a boundary
on the leg stump, Younis turns it away to short fine leg for a single
short outside the off stump, Younis rocks back and cuts it past covers for a brace
fuller outside the off stump, Younis brings out the drive again but straight to the extra cover fielder
slower delivery on the off stump as Younis does a Richards by picking it from off and whips it away to midwicket boundary
full toss outside off, Younis forces it off the backfoot past point for a boundary
full toss on the off stump this time round as Younis punches it down to long off to pick up his third boundary of the over
fuller on the off stump, Younis pushes it to mid on for a single
short outside the off stump to begin with as Younis cuts it to backward point for his fourth boundary off five balls
on a good length outside off, pushes it to deep extra cover for a single
outside the off stump, pushes to cover
fuller on the off stump, Misbah pushes it to mid on for a single
on the off stump, swings and gets an outside edge to third man for a boundary
drifts onto the legs as Younis effortlessly flicks it away to fine leg for a couple
fuller on the middle stump but Misbah is moving across as the ball is bowled and  pushes it away to square leg for a boundary
fuller on the off stump, Misbah comes onto the frontfoot and drives to cover
fuller on the middle stump as Misbah drives to long on for a couple
on the leg stump, defends on the frontfoot
on the off stump, pushes it to backward point for a single
fuller on the middle stump as he pushes it to mid on for a single
on the off stump, defends on the frontfoot to fetch a single
short outside the off stump, Misbah cuts it to deep backward point for a single
fuller on the off stump as Younis chips it away to deep midwicket for a couple
fuller on the off stump as Younis brings the drive out again to long off for a single
outside the off stump, pushes it a little bit faster as Misbah looks to cut it but misses
take that! Younis comes down the track and lofts it away over midwicket for a one bounce boundary. Looking in pristine touch is Younis
fuller outside the off stump, Younis pushes it to long off for a single
full toss on the leg stump as Misbah pushes it to long on for a single. Looks a little uncomfortable though
fuller outside off, drives it to cover
outside the off stump, Younis steers but a misfield allows him a couple
fuller on the off stump, drives it to long on for a single
fuller on the middle stump as Younis tamely lobs the ball back to the bowler to end what was an attacking innings
fuller outside the off stump as Malik drives to extra cover for a single
on the off stump, Misbah gets onto the backfoot as he turns it to deep midwicket for a couple
on the leg stump, M/isbah guides it to fine leg for a single
fires it on the leg stump as Malik pushes it to midwicket for a single
on the leg stump, pushes it to square leg for a single
fuller outside the off stump, drives to long off for a single
on the middle stump, Malik pushes it to midwicket for a single
fuller outside the off stump, drives to long off for another single
fuller on the off stump as Malik gets into the act now by whipping it away to deep midwicket for a boundary
full toss outside the off stump as Malik comes down the track and drives it to mid off
on the off stump, Malik covers the line of the delivery and gets right under it as he sends it sailing over long on for a huge six
outside the off stump, cut to point for a couple
fuller on the off stump, Misbah drives it back to the bowler
outside the off stump, drives it to cover
on the leg stump, pushes it to long on for a single
on a good length outside the off stump as Malik comes down the track and  lofts over extra cover for a huge six
pushes to cover for a single
full on off stump, he looks to on-drive but mistimes it to cover
comes forward and drives to mid-off for a quick single
there's a shot and a half! The Misbah special, down on one knee and a clean strike over long-on for maxium!
gets forward, then back, and works it past the gap for a quick two
comes onto the front foot and pushes into the covers, there's a man there
comes forward and on-drives down the ground for one
another dab to point, and the tip-and-run gets him a single
punched down the ground, the sweeper does well to keep them to one
tries an expansive reverse-sweep but short third man dives well
gives himself room to drive over the top and the ball drops safely
gets outside off and hammers a big shot over deep midwicket
shuffles around and tucks it away past midwicket and sprints back
well bowled, tight stuff in the blockhole and its punched back
huge hit! Malik dances down and heaves the full toss over midwicket
makes room and slashes an arm ball out to deep cover ropes
thats a shot! Backs away two feet outside leg stump and slams this over the bowlers' hands for a flat hit
gone! That one skips by his bat as he attempts a huge slog, Dhiman collects and whips off the bails with Malik's back foot still outside the line, marginally
Afridi's away with a quick push into the gap between two men
gets back and pushes one towards midwicket
exposes all the stumps and cuts a short one through the covers
well bowled, good drift into Afridi and he pushes off the back foot
skips down, Shakib sees him and fires it short so he plays it back to him
fraction too short and he pulls past mid-on for a comfortable single
gets a flat one and works it across the line past mid-on for one
huge hit, comes down and slams this downtown for a big one!
he gets back and tries to cut it fine, mistiming the stroke for one
thats a wide, very far outside the off stump
poor bowling, fired down the pads this time for another wide
swings at a wide one and inside-edges past leg stump

well done in the deep! Afridi kneels down and slogs this off the pads down to deep midwicket, where Ferhad Reza gets underneath it, catches it, but loses his balance and throws the ball back as he falls onto his back over the ropes ... a fantastic effort
now thats six! Misbah slogs this one flat out to the sweeper on the on long-off ropes, who takes it but cannot control himself this time
tame end to the innings of Afridi as he looks to hoick it to midwicket and is castled
fuller outside the off stump, Alam drives it back to the bowler
fuller outside the off stump as Alam moves across and punches it to long on for a single
short on the leg stump as Misbah tucks it away to fine leg for a single
full outside the off stump, pushes to long on for a single
pushes to mid on for a single
fuller outside the off stump as Misbah shuffles back and across and smashes it to long off but a poor fielding effort by Razzak fetches him a boundary
slower outside the off stump, Misbah runs it down to third man for a single
fuller outside the off stump, Alam looks to loft it away on the leg side but gets an inside edge to fine leg for a single
fuller outside the off stump as Misbah goes inside out and does not get enough wood on it as it falls in a no mans land and allows Misbah to take a couple
fuller on the middle stump this time round as Misbah lofts it away to long on where an athletic effort by Tamim limits them to a couple
short outside the off stump, cut to cover for a single
on the middle stump, Misbah forces it to midwicket as Mashrafe is seen being attended to
short on the off stump, Misbah pulls the screws out of it as he pulls it to square leg for a huge six
on the leg stump, plays a lofted drive to mid on for a single
fuller on the off stump as Alam strokes it past the bowler to long off for a boundary

on the middle stump and fuller in length as Alam bludgeons it hard and only succeeds in getting it to  long on where an unbalanced Mahmudullah relays the ball over the ropes as double pain is inflicted on Shahadat
on the off stump as Alam slogs and gets an inside edge to fine leg for three runs
